                            <p>He was an eminent chemistry lecturer in the most famous college in Anantapur, which inspired him to enhance the quality of education among the rural youth.</p>
							<p>He started educational institutions in 1991 through “Sri Balaji Educational Society” in varied courses such as Junior colleges, D.Ed, T.T.C, B.Ed, Degree & PG Colleges. To enhance vocationalization of education he started professional courses such as pharmacy, Engineering, M.B.A, and M.C.A.</p>
						<p>In short span, Sri Balaji Educational Society has put up good strength and influence providing ample employment opportunities to the educated youth of Anantapur district.</p>
	
